   104‚Üí## Installation and Docs
   105‚Üí
   106‚ÜíInstall using `go get github.com/hashicorp/go-multierror`.
   107‚Üí
   108‚ÜíFull documentation is available at
   109‚Üíhttps://pkg.go.dev/github.com/hashicorp/go-multierror
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
   111‚Üí### Requires go version 1.13 or newer
   112‚Üí
   113‚Üí`go-multierror` requires go version 1.13 or newer. Go 1.13 introduced
   114‚Üí[error wrapping](https://golang.org/doc/go1.13#error_wrapping), which
   115‚Üíthis library takes advantage of.
   116‚Üí
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
   129‚Üí## Usage
   130‚Üí
   131‚Üígo-multierror is easy to use and purposely built to be unobtrusive in
   132‚Üíexisting Go applications/libraries that may not be aware of it.
   133‚Üí
